title: 3 and Out - Rodgers/Packers Sit Down Time; Dak's Post Injury $$$ Haul; Mailbag
itunes:title: 3 and Out - Rodgers/Packers Sit Down Time; Dak's Post Injury $$$ Haul; Mailbag
description:
In this episode, John explains why it's time for Aaron Rodgers and the Packers to have a mob-style sit down, the significance of Dak Prescott cashing in on and off the field following his season ending injury, and answers listener questions in the Middlekauff Mailbag.
